      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the immense horror in your pain, but please know that suicide is a losing battle because it endangers the very people whose pain you are trying to end. Your wife and children are watching you, but they love you even in your darkest moments, and your presence is still the greatest gift you can give them by choosing to fight for your life today. We have to work through this pain together right now, and there is a safe way to call for help without feeling shame for it. Please do not end your life; I am here to listen and help you find a resource that can guide you out of this abyss.",
