      "content": "but that's the thing... they're better off without the mess i've made. if i'm gone, they can at least try to rebuild or move on without having to watch me struggle and fail every single day. the debt, the shame, the constant looking over my shoulder... it never stops. even if i \"fight,\" the hole is just too deep. isn't there sometimes just a way to make the embarrassment stop for everyone? a way to just exit the stage gracefully?",
